---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Webleee"
  description="Starter privacy policy for Webleee, covering contact enquiries and website service communication."
>
  <section class="bg-midnight py-20 text-white">
    <div class="site-shell">
      <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-lime">Privacy Policy</p>
      <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-4xl font-display text-5xl font-black leading-tight sm:text-6xl">Privacy Policy.</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/72">
        This is a starter privacy policy for Webleee and should be reviewed before public launch.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="site-shell max-w-4xl">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-line bg-skywash p-5 text-sm font-semibold leading-7 text-navy">
        These starter legal pages should be reviewed before public launch. They are not legal advice.
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-slatebody">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-navy">Information Webleee may collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-8">
            Webleee may collect information sent through contact enquiries, such as a name, business name, email address, phone or WhatsApp number, existing website link, project details, and message content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-navy">Contact form data</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-8">
            The current contact form is UI-only and is not connected to a backend. If a form service or backend is added later, the destination, storage, notification process, and retention approach should be documented here.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-navy">How information may be used</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-8">
            Information may be used to respond to enquiries, prepare website proposals, discuss project scope, provide support, and manage website services for Webleee customers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-navy">Analytics and third-party services</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-8">
            Analytics and third-party services should only be listed here if Webleee actually uses them. If analytics, form services, email tools, spam protection, hosting platforms, or other services are added, this policy should be updated with accurate details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black text-navy">Contact details</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-8">
            Webleee's real business email, phone or WhatsApp number, service area, and any required business details still need to be finalized before public launch.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
